N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 441.233 - Other operating revenue

State Regulations

Other operating revenue includes revenue from nonpatient
care services to patients and sales and activities to persons other than
patients, and the value of donated commodities. Notes
